ere are some simple tips:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Lubricate the springs<\/strong> every six months with a silicone-based spray<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Keep the area dry and clean<\/strong> to prevent rust and corrosion<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Avoid slamming the door<\/strong> shut manually<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Don\u2019t overload the door<\/strong> with insulation or hardware<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Schedule yearly maintenance checks<\/strong> with a pro<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Replace both springs at the same time<\/strong> to maintain balance<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Our techs are happy to perform a full-system tune-up when replacing your springs. A little preventive care goes a long way!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Austin Homeowners Choose Garage Up for Spring Repairs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>At Garage Up Austin, garage door repair isn\u2019t a side hustle\u2014it\u2019s what we do. And we do it with pride, precision, and professionalism.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\u2019s why homeowners across Austin trust us:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Locally owned<\/strong> and operated with deep roots in the Austin community<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Same-day service<\/strong>, even on weekends and holidays<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Licensed and insured<\/strong> with certified technicians<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>5-star Google reviews<\/strong> and glowing customer testimonials<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Trusted in every Austin neighborhood<\/strong> from Zilker to Brushy Creek<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019re not a national chain or faceless franchise\u2014we\u2019re your neighbors. We know Austin homes, weather, and style. And we treat your garage like it\u2019s our own.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Don\u2019t Let a Broken Spring Stop You \u2013 Call Garage Up Austin Today<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A broken garage spring isn\u2019t just an inconvenience\u2014it\u2019s a safety issue that can bring your wh